<p>The results for my game jam submission were pretty average overall. Since my main focus has always been on making games that are fun to play, I never expected audio or artwork to be my strong suits — and I knew going in that those categories would likely score lower.</p>
<p>Looking specifically at the <strong>Enjoyment</strong> category, my game ranked <strong>2992 out of 9651 entries</strong>. Not exactly a top-tier placement, but definitely far from the bottom.</p>]]></description>
